{"tid":272741,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【比特幣狂潮】Bitcoin又起飛！ 突破2,800美元創新高","createTime":"2017-06-06T05:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T05:01:39.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"620906fca7fef4bc7f41c110a26a6cdfd46dcfaa","tid":272741,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170606/large/1496723218_e775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170606%2Flarge%2F1496723218_e775.jpg&h=13ceda03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣（Bitcoin）又創新高，今日曾急飆7.8%，成功突破2,800美元大關，高見2,871美元，截至本港時間中午報2,813美元，升5.6%。<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin自4月份得到日本政府「認證」後，價格飛漲，雖然5月尾上試2,800美元失敗後，曾急回至2,200美元附近水平，踏入6月重拾升勢，至今兩個月時間已升值約一倍。日本現時有部分零售點及航空公司已接受Bitcoin支付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56789991&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56789991%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c628a164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56789991%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&h=b95ea25f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56789991&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606</a>"}]}